From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Stefan Reinauer <stefan.reinauer@coreboot.org>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 21:10:00 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] build: drop QEMU 11 pvg option for QEMU 9

QEMU 11 has a pvg Meson feature option, but QEMU 9.2.4 does not. The
base QEMU-UAE patch deck follows the QEMU 11 source branch, so keep this
version-specific configure adjustment in the QEMU 9 overlay.
---
 configure-qemu-uae | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/configure-qemu-uae b/configure-qemu-uae
index d5452a2721..631fe4eb4 100755
--- a/configure-qemu-uae
+++ b/configure-qemu-uae
@@ -43,7 +43,6 @@ EXTRA_CFLAGS="$EXTRA_CFLAGS -g -gcodeview"
     --disable-cocoa \
     --disable-vnc \
     --disable-dbus-display \
-    --disable-pvg \
     --disable-coreaudio \
     --audio-drv-list= \
     --disable-auth-pam \
-- 
2.50.1 (Apple Git-155)

